conceptquiz

Project overview

This is an educational project. With the sole purpose of learning by doing, I start this type of quiz to learn concepts commonly used in computing, programming and systems engineering, but it can be used with a dictionary of terms of any matter or subject.

I am taking a Python online course and need to familiarize myself with these terms.

I'm getting a great guide from GEMINI, although most of the time it offers snippets of code that doesn't work, but it gives me a good example of the syntax and built-in functions that can be used.

I must say that I am using tkinter library for personal and non-commercial purposes.

About using the listed files:

main.py is the main script.

DICTIO_coding_concepts_eduardo is the dictionary used by the main script.

It can be used as a visual/written study tool like flashcards, with a dictionary full of any given data, for any area of ​​university study, unlike GEMINI LIVE that can now apply any SPOKEN questionnaire you want, like an interactive chat, only spoken.

Am still in the process of creating a new desktop icon for it since I somehow made it once and now I need to redo all the steps for the new version of the code I keep improving. It also needs 2 more elements I'm working on right now: 1.- Insert some 8-bit music directly in the program.
